### 1. Health Check
# Ensures the gRPC Health Check service is active and the FHIR Store is reachable.
GRPC http://localhost:5001/grpc.health.v1.Health/Check
{
  "service": "FhirStore"
}

### 2. Get Patient Identity
# Fetches a standard test patient from the HAPI R5 server.
GRPC http://localhost:5001/FhirGrpcGateway.Server.PatientApi/GetPatient
{
  "id": "example"
}

### 3. Search for Observations (Vitals)
# Queries blood pressure or heart rate data for a specific patient.
GRPC http://localhost:5001/FhirGrpcGateway.Server.ObservationApi/GetPatientObservations
{
  "patient_id": "example",
  "limit": 5
}

### 4. List Active Conditions
# Retrieves the current problem list for an AI/MCP agent to process.
GRPC http://localhost:5001/FhirGrpcGateway.Server.ConditionApi/GetPatientConditions
{
  "patient_id": "example"
}

### 5. Stream Full Medical Record ($everything)
# Test the server-side streaming capability for bulk data transfer.
GRPC http://localhost:5001/FhirGrpcGateway.Server.PatientApi/GetEverything
{
  "id": "example"
}